headline: Carmakers Get Blindsided by Tariff Relief—Heard on the Street
summary: The fact these companies seemed blindsided is a reminder that they face a difficult and uncertain future.  Meanwhile, Commerce Secretary Howard Lutnick has confirmed Trump will announce on Tuesday a softening of auto tariffs.
